msgstr "Introduction"

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/espressif/esp32-s2.rst:8 0d68ff29e8844dc996c1f0b45c3f1d39
msgid "ESP32-S2系列模组的芯片ESP32-S2芯片搭载 Xtensa® 32 位 LX7 单核处理器，工作频率高达 240 MHz。芯片支持二次开发，无需使用其它微控制器或处理器。该芯片内置 320 KB SRAM/128 KB ROM，可通过 SPI/QSPI/OSPI 等接口外接 flash 和 RAM。ESP32-S2 支持多种低功耗工作状态，能够满足各种应用场景的功耗需求。芯片所特有的精细时钟门控功能、动态电压时钟频率调节功能、射频输出功率可调节功能等特性，可以实现通信距离、通信速率和功耗之间的最佳平衡。"
msgstr "The ESP32-S2 chip used in the ESP32-S2 series modules features an Xtensa® 32-bit LX7 single-core processor with an operating frequency of up to 240MHz. The chip supports secondary development without the need for an additional microcontroller or processor. It has built-in 320KB SRAM and 128KB ROM, and can connect to external Flash and RAM through interfaces such as SPI, QSPI, and OSPI. The ESP32-S2 supports multiple low-power operating states to meet the power consumption requirements of various application scenarios. Its unique features, such as fine-grained clock gating, dynamic voltage and frequency scaling, and adjustable RF output power, enable an optimal balance among communication distance, communication rate, and power consumption."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/espressif/esp32-s2.rst:10 8758537a0dd14c62a5beef6a0445fce2
msgid "ESP32-S2系列模组ESP32-S2芯片提供丰富的外设接口，包括 SPI，I2S，UART，I2C，LED PWM，LCD 接口，Camera 接口，ADC，DAC，触摸传感器，温度传感器和多达 43 个 GPIO。它支持芯片外围扩展 PSRAM，ESP-12K 模组可以选配 PSRAM。此外，它还包括一个全速 USB On-The-Go (OTG)接口，可以支持使用 USB 通信。"
msgstr "The ESP32-S2 chip used in the ESP32-S2 series modules provides rich peripheral interfaces, including SPI, I2S, UART, I2C, LED PWM, LCD interface, camera interface, ADC, DAC, touch sensor, temperature sensor, and up to 43 GPIOs. It supports external PSRAM expansion around the chip, and the ESP-12K module can be optionally equipped with PSRAM. In addition, it includes a full-speed USB On-The-Go (OTG) interface, supporting communication via USB."

#: ../../source/docs/development-environment/espressif/esp32-s2.rst:12 1934c6f8eed2454bb32c0332a12ec133
msgid "乐鑫官网出售有ESP32-S2 Beta芯片和ESP32-S2芯片，而ESP32-S2 Beta芯片与最终的ESP32-S2不同，Beta芯片是有限的工程样本，因此并非所有功能都可用。我司并没有出售ESP32-S2 Beta芯片的模组！"
msgstr "Espressif officially sells both ESP32-S2 Beta chips and ESP32-S2 chips. However, the ESP32-S2 Beta chip is different from the final ESP32-S2. The Beta chip is a limited engineering sample, so not all functions are available. Our company does not sell modules based on the ESP32-S2 Beta chip!"

